### 3. FETCH STOCK INFO
GET http://localhost:3000/stock/AAPL

### 4. BUY TRADE
POST http://localhost:3000/trade-api/trade
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "symbol": "AAPL",
    "type": "BUY",
    "quantity": 2
}

### 5. GET PORTFOLIO
GET http://localhost:3000/portfolio-api/portfolio

### 6. GET PORTFOLIO SUMMARY
GET http://localhost:3000/portfolio-api/portfolio/summary

### 7. GET PORTFOLIO HISTORY
GET http://localhost:3000/portfolio-api/portfolio/history

### 8. GET TRADE HISTORY
GET http://localhost:3000/trade-api/trades

### 9. SELL 1 AAPL
POST http://localhost:3000/trade-api/trade
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "symbol": "AAPL",
    "type": "SELL",
    "quantity": 1
}

### 10. SELL MORE THAN HELD — should return 400
POST http://localhost:3000/trade-api/trade
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "symbol": "AAPL",
    "type": "SELL",
    "quantity": 999
}

### 11. BUY INSUFFICIENT FUNDS — should return 400
POST http://localhost:3000/trade-api/trade
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "symbol": "AAPL",
    "type": "BUY",
    "quantity": 999999
}

### 12. INVALID TYPE — should return 400
POST http://localhost:3000/trade-api/trade
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "symbol": "AAPL",
    "type": "HOLD",
    "quantity": 1
}